      <h3 class="c-entry-box-base__headline"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="article" href="https://www.theringer.com/2020/4/20/21228570/ferris-buellers-day-off-with-bill-simmons-sean-fennessey-and-chris-ryan">‘Ferris Bueller’s Day Off’ With Bill Simmons, Sean Fennessey, and Chris Ryan</a></h3>
    

  
    
      
        <p class="c-entry-box-base__dek p-dek c-entry-box-base__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek">Stay home and rewatch this 1986 classic starring Matthew Broderick, Alan Ruck, and Mia Sara</p>
      
    

    

  
    
      
      
        
