      <h3 class="c-entry-box-base__headline"><a data-chorus-optimize-field="hed" data-analytics-link="article" href="https://www.theringer.com/the-bill-simmons-podcast/2020/4/20/21227679/mjs-doc-tuas-draft-stock-l-t-vs-rice-and-the-93-knicks-bulls-battle-with-ryen-russillo">MJ’s Doc, Tua’s Draft Stock, L.T. vs. Rice, and the ’93 Knicks-Bulls Battle With Ryen Russillo</a></h3>
    

  
    
      
        <p class="c-entry-box-base__dek p-dek c-entry-box-base__dek" data-chorus-optimize-field="dek">Bill and Ryen discuss the first two episodes of ESPN’s ‘The Last Dance,’ the NFL draft, and more</p>
      
    

    

  
    
      
      
        
