            <a href="https://www.theringer.com/authors/bill-simmons" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Bill Simmons</span></a> and <a href="https://www.theringer.com/authors/ryen-russillo" data-analytics-link="author-name"><span class="c-byline__author-name">Ryen Russillo</span></a>
          
